            </div>
            <div class="col-md-7 pt-5 order-2 order-md-1" data-aos="fade-right">
                <h3> </h3>
                <p class="font-italic">
                    Most older women accessing
                    homelessness services seek general
                    services (82% of women) but many
                    also need domestic violence assistance
                    (35%), long-term accommodation
                    (31%) and tenure assistance
                    (29%).However, few existing services
                    are specifically designed to meet the
                    needs of older women.
                </p>
                <p>
                    In this case, if you have the concern about suffering family violence
                    as an elder woman, do not be afraid, try to get support from our
                    service or other organizations. Please remember you are not alone,
                    you don’t have to face this situation by yourself.
                </p>
